## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of human-induced climate change. The data is primarily sourced from essays and reports, which may not reflect the most current scientific consensus. Additionally, the complexity of climate systems means that attributing specific changes to human activities involves uncertainties. Further research and updated data from scientific bodies like the IPCC are recommended for a more comprehensive understanding.

